3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for medical image segmentation, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with segmentation of medical images, which can be considered as a type of multimedia data. 
5. cs.MS (Medical Imaging): The paper deals with medical image segmentation, which falls under the domain of medical imaging.
